---
import ContentSection from "./content-section.astro";
import Btn from "./button.astro";
import Modal from "./modal.astro";
import Ai from "./ai.astro";
---

<ContentSection
  title="期待一起合作"
  subtitle="Let's work together"
  id="Contact"
>
  <Fragment slot="description">
    如果您正在寻求与众不同的品牌设计方案，欢迎随时与我们取得联系。无论您有任何关于设计的需求或问题，我们都乐意倾听并为您提供专业的咨询服务。
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="description-below">
    If you're seeking unique branding solutions, feel free to reach out to us
    anytime. Whatever your requirements or queries about branding design, we are
    eager to listen and provide professional consultation services.
  </Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="content">
    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <Btn btnText="Contact Us 👋" btnAltText="联系我们 👋" url="/contact" />
      <Modal btnText="→ AI Assistant🦄" btnAltText="→ 咨询AI助手🦄" mTitle="格润达理工作室AI助手" mId="ai" mFooter="⚠️ 注：所有回答均为AI生成，可能会犯错，请核查重要信息，如有疑问请通过其他方式联系我们。">
        <Ai />
      </Modal>
    </div>
  </Fragment>
</ContentSection>
